Package civitas.celestis.world

Interface World

All Superinterfaces:
Unique
All Known Implementing Classes:
RealisticWorld
public interface World extends Unique

World

The World interface represents a virtual world containing various BaseObjects. It defines methods to manage and interact with the objects within the world.

    • updateOverlaps

      void updateOverlaps()
      Updates the list of overlapping objects within the world.

      This method should be called to refresh the list of object overlaps based on the current positions and orientations of objects within the world.

      After calling this method, the list of overlapping objects can be retrieved using the getOverlaps() method.
